00:21:41,537 --> 00:21:42,468
No.

282
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:52,213
What was it...

283
00:21:54,167 --> 00:21:56,458
...that I wanted to hear?

284
00:22:10,385 --> 00:22:11,683
Cut. Okay!

285
00:22:11,768 --> 00:22:12,748
-Thank you.
-Great job!

286
00:22:12,833 --> 00:22:13,799
Thank you!

287
00:22:13,884 --> 00:22:15,588
Thank you.

288
00:22:16,881 --> 00:22:18,288
Great job, everyone.

289
00:22:19,201 --> 00:22:20,516
Thank you.

290
00:22:21,262 --> 00:22:23,012
Great job, everyone.

291
00:22:25,749 --> 00:22:26,779
Mr. Lee...

292
00:22:27,711 --> 00:22:29,294
Thank you for all your trouble.

293
00:22:30,610 --> 00:22:33,319
Thank you for giving me a chance.

294
00:22:34,421 --> 00:22:35,521
And for trusting me.

295
00:22:36,938 --> 00:22:38,337
Looking at you...

296
00:22:39,609 --> 00:22:41,302
I thought...

297
00:22:42,219 --> 00:22:44,342
...maybe I'm the one who's changed.

298
